Class Report

  • Constructor Details

    • Report

      protected Report​(java.lang.String id, java.time.LocalDateTime date, java.lang.String primaryDescription, java.lang.String secondaryDescription, java.lang.String locationDescription, java.lang.Boolean domestic, java.lang.Integer xCoord, java.lang.Integer yCoord, java.lang.Double latitude, java.lang.Double longitude)
      Initializes a Report object.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier for the report object
      date - A required field which contains the year, month, day and time of the crime
      primaryDescription - A required field which contains the primary description of the crime
      secondaryDescription - A required field which contains the more descriptive secondary description of the crime
      locationDescription - An optional field which contains the description of the location where the crime occurred
      domestic - An optional field which contains if the crime was domestic
      xCoord - An optional field which is has the x-coordinate of where the crime occurred
      yCoord - An optional field which is has the y-coordinate of where the crime occurred
      latitude - An optional field which is has the latitude of where the crime occurred
      longitude - An optional field which is has the longitude of where the crime occurred
